### AI Agent Travel Planner - API Test File
### Use this with VS Code REST Client extension or any HTTP client
### Make sure the Azure Functions app is running on localhost:7071

@baseUrl = http://localhost:7071/api
@contentType = application/json

### Step 1: Create Travel Plan
POST {{baseUrl}}/travel-planner
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "userName": "Test User",
  "preferences": "Beach vacation with cultural experiences and great food",
  "durationInDays": 7,
  "budget": "$3000-$5000",
  "travelDates": "July 15-22, 2025",
  "specialRequirements": "Vegetarian dining options preferred"
}

### Step 2: Check Status (replace YOUR_INSTANCE_ID with the ID from step 1 response)
GET {{baseUrl}}/travel-planner/status/YOUR_INSTANCE_ID_HERE

### Step 3: Approve Travel Plan (replace YOUR_INSTANCE_ID with the ID from step 1 response)
POST {{baseUrl}}/travel-planner/approve/YOUR_INSTANCE_ID_HERE
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "approved": true,
  "comments": "The plan looks great! Please proceed with booking."
}
